@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p>At <strong>Courier Service</strong>, we prioritize the privacy of our customers. This Privacy Policy document outlines the types of information we collect and how we use it responsibly. By using our services, you consent to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.</p>

    <h3>1. Information Collection</h3>
    <p>We collect various types of information, including:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, age, phone number, and addresses to facilitate shipment deliveries.</li>
        <li><strong>Shipment Details:</strong> Information about the items being shipped, weight, delivery preferences, and more.</li>
        <li><strong>Transaction Information:</strong> UPI transaction IDs for payment verification purposes.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>2. Use of Information</h3>
    <p>Your information is used to provide and improve our courier services. Specifically, we use it to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Process your shipment requests and ensure timely delivery.</li>
        <li>Communicate with you regarding delivery updates and support.</li>
        <li>Validate payment information securely.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>3. Data Security</h3>
    <p>We implement strong security measures to protect your personal information. All sensitive data is handled with care, and only authorized personnel have access to it.</p>

    <h3>4. Sharing of Information</h3>
    <p>Your personal information is never shared with third parties except as required for delivery processing (e.g., with delivery partners) or by law.</p>

    <h3>5. Changes to the Privacy Policy</h3>
    <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

    <p class="mt-4"><em>Last Updated: November 4, 2024</em></p>
</div>
